text: Craig Merren (born 6 November 1966) is a Caymanian former cyclist. He competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics, 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Caymanian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of the Cayman Islands Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
